import React from "react"; import "./singleReport.scss"; const SingleReport = ({ report }) => { return (
Patient's name:

{report.firstName} {report.lastName}

Age:

{report.age}

DOB:

{report.dob}

Sex:

{report.sex}

Address:

{report.address}

Status:

{report.status}

Treatment By:

{report.doctor}

Date:

{report.createdAt}

); }; export default SingleReport;
